                                                            ___
      * Bitmap gamma test example. Of       ,---.        /""`_,'
        course it does not work yet,        |    `\``""-;   /
        because some dirty old pig          \   /`\\     ';'
        implemented a cucul_powf()        .')   |     __   \
        function that only works         / (`  /     /(O\. _|
        with integer exponents.       .-`|  `"`      `    .-\_
